&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/USA-BEVERLY-HILLS-THE-BELVEDERE-OFFER-LOGO-MEDIUM.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-4587&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/USA-BEVERLY-HILLS-THE-BELVEDERE-OFFER-LOGO-MEDIUM.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;USA- BEVERLY HILLS- THE BELVEDERE- OFFER- LOGO MEDIUM&quot; width=&quot;130&quot; height=&quot;50&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The only &lt;strong&gt;AAA Five Diamond&lt;/strong&gt; restaurant in Southern California for 20 consecutive years, The Belvedere offers both indoor and outdoor seating as well as a private dining room. Enjoy the modern elegance of The Belvedere for breakfast, lunch, dinner, Sunday brunch and lovely afternoon tea. Attire is business casual.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please book online at &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.opentable.com/the-belvedere-reservations-beverly-hills?rtype=ism&amp;amp;restref=2282&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;The Belvedere website&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;or contact The Belvedere by phone at +1-310-975-2736 or email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:diningpbh@peninsula.com&quot;&gt;diningpbh@peninsula.com&lt;/a&gt; to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation Policy- If you&rsquo;re not able to make your dining date, please cancel the reservation as a courtesy to the restaurant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: Please contact the restaurant by phone or email 24 hours prior to your dining date to reconfirm. Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection reservation. If not reconfirmed your reservation may be given away if need arises&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating restaurant merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

